This example represents four different images randomly displayed on the screen in a grid of 3 rows with 5 images on each row. The interactivity is basic click on the button "KICK IT". By clicking the button the example makes the images change in a style, which assembles a slot machine. The interactivity is made by an EventListenener of clicking with the left button of the mouse. Moreover, with interacting with the screen using mouse hovering, the mouse leaves a big white trail to indicate easiliy it's position on the screen. The style of the button "KICK IT", which starts the example of a slot machine, is taking place in a black bar in order to be perceived by the user as an interactive button. The example could be use in sort of online gambling games with slot machines for example.